# commands to prepare for I- and R-channel exposures
 camera close
 camera open
 camera load
 camera native CSH
 camera native PON 
 camera native ERS 1000 1000
 camera imsize I 1220 4114 0 100 1 1 
 camera imsize R 1220 4114 0 100 1 1 
 camera native WRM 0x400004 2040
 camera exptime 0
 camera readout I U2
 camera readout R U1
 camera useframes false
 camera mex true
 camera shutter enable
 camera basename ngps_$1
 camera fitsnaming number
 camera native EPG 500
